         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Excelsior Hotel ¶ Bourke Street ¶ Melbourne, 13 June 1870 ¶  ¶ Dr von Mueller ¶ Esteemed Sir,...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">70.06.13</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From C. Grevsmühl</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M106.20, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Excelsiors Hotel</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Bourke Street</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">den 13 Juni 1870.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Herr v Müller Dr</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Geehrter Herr!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Im Auftrage des Melb. deutschen Turnvereins habe ich die Ehre Ihnen mitzutheilen, dass Sie in der letzten halbjährlichen Generalversammlung, vom Vorstande als Ehren-Mitglied, vorgeschlagen, und von der Versammlung aufgenommen, wurden. Möchten Sie so freundlich sein, und mich umgehend Ihren vollständigen Namen zu kommen lassen. </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Um alle Irrthümer im Diplom zu vermeiden, bin ich gezwungen Sie mit der letzten Bitte zu belästigen.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Hochachtungsvoll</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>C. A. Grevsmühl</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Schriftwart d. M. deutsch. Turnvereins</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Excelsior Hotel</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Bourke Street</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne, 13 June 1870</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Dr von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Esteemed Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honour to inform you on behalf of the Melbourne German Gymnastics Club, that at their last half-yearly general meeting you were proposed as Honorary Member by the Council and accepted by the meeting.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Several years before this, M was described in a report in Melbourne’s German-language newspaper </seg>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Germania</seg>
                     <seg style="">, 17 May 1866, p. 1169, as an honorary member of the Gymnastics Club. This, however, was probably a mistake; no other evidence of an earlier election has been found.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> Would you be so kind and let me have your complete name by return mail?</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>To avoid any errors in the certificate I am obliged to trouble you with this request.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Respectfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>C. A. Grevsmühl</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Secretary, Melbourne German Gymnastics Club.</p>
         </div>
